messages.message:
Hey, I took the ANZx team through some Q4 roadmap additions today. The two main gaps they still are pressing for are:
1. RAI (and other external systems) integration. I'm not sure if this is the best ticket or not: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-2940
2. Prompt Versioning: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-2939. 
    a. They actually want a step further which would be GitHub style integrations where you can track changes, user logging of changes (who changed what), roll back, control permissions etc
    b. The pain point they've described is having large teams working on projects and people stepping on each other's toes/making changes when they shouldn't be
